recoursemech: If an individual has any questions or concerns about our Safe Harbor practices, we ask them to write or email us at our contact information provided. We will investigate and attempt to resolve complaints and disputes regarding use and disclosure of Personal Information in accordance with the Safe Harbor Principles. If after contacting us, your complaint or dispute has not been resolved, your complaint will be referred to the Data Protection Panel comprised of EU data protection regulators or to the Swiss Data Protection and Information Commissioner. Health Flights Solutions commits to following the determination and advice of these bodies.
